This all works, but there is no documentation yet.

Basically you'll need to be able to install and use a procmailrc file and a
bunch of other stuff.

If you're itching to get started, take a look at procmailrc.sample and start
filling in the blanks. It's more tedious than it is hard.

--

Requirements:

* http://search.cpan.org/dist/Net-Flickr-API-1.69 (or higher)

* http://github.com/straup/filtr

* (other stuff...)

--

See also:

* http://www.aaronland.info/weblog/2006/07/31/baconmelon/#filtr

* http://rcrowley.org/2007/11/08/introducing-curvr/

* http://rcrowley.org/2007/12/30/postfixing-your-email-life#comments

* http://github.com/rcrowley/curvr/
